metadata.name: I Will Never See Myself Perform Live
metadata.description: Renaissance Malfunction is a unique NFT collection that redefines the art spectrum. Fusing classic realism with modern glitch, grain, and trash art elements, each 1/1 piece serves as a daring statement about the beauty of imperfection. This collection invites you to explore a reimagination of the Renaissance, where traditional artistry collides with digital disruption.
